Harry GLIMP v. Charles BROSCH, Jr., et al. No. 6173. United States Court of Appeals Tenth Circuit. Nov. 18,1959. Harry D. Moreland, Tulsa, Okl., for appellant. Ungerman, Grabel, Ungerman, Leiter & Unruh, Charles A. Whitebook and John T. Gibson, Tulsa, Okl., and Jack B. Sellers, Drumright, Okl., for appellees.

Before MURRAH, Chief Judge, BREITENSTEIN, Circuit Judge, and CHRISTENSON, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed on motion of appellant.
